th Rovers F.C.|Raith Rovers]]\n|[[2013\u201314 Kilmarnock F.C. season|2013\u201314]]<ref>{{Soccerbase season|id=40507|season=2013|accessdate=2 January 2018}}</ref>\n|rowspan=\"5\"|[[Scottish Championship]]\n||14||0||1||0||0||0||0||0||15||0\n|-\n|[[Rangers F.C.|Rangers]]\n|[[2014\u201315 Rangers F.C. season|2014\u201315]]<ref>{{Soccerbase season|id=40507|season=2014|accessdate=2 January 2018}}</ref>\n||7||0||1||0||1||0||0||0||9||0\n|-\n|[[Queen of the South F.C.|Queen of the South]]\n|[[2016\u201317 Queen of the South F.C. season|2016\u201317]]<ref>{{Soccerbase season|id=40507|season=2016|accessdate=2 January 2018}}</ref>\n||35||0||1||0||6||0||4<ref group=lower-alpha name=\"SCC\"/>||0||46||0\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Dunfermline Athletic F.C.|Dunfermline Athletic]]\n|[[2017\u201318 Dunfermline Athletic F.C. season|2017\u201318]]<ref>{{Soccerbase season|id=40507|season=2017|accessdate=2 January 2018}}</ref>\n||18||0||1||0||0||0||2<ref group=lower-alpha name=\"Play-offs\">Appearances in the [[Scottish Premiership]] play-offs</ref>||0||21||0\n|-\n|[[2018\u201319 Dunfermline Athletic F.C. season|2018\u201319]]<ref>{{Soccerbase season|id=40507|season=2018|accessdate=17 May 2018}}</ref>\n||21||0||1||0||4||0||2||0||28||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!39!!0!!2!!0!!4!!0!!4!!0!!49!!0\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career Total\n!206!!0!!11!!0!!19!!0!!13!!0!!249!!0\n|}\n\n{{reflist|group=lower-alpha}}\n\n==Honours==\n\n===Club===\n;Queen of the South\n*[[Scottish Challenge Cup]] (1): [[2013 Scottish Challenge Cup Final|2012\u201313]]\n*[[Scottish Second Division]] (1): [[2012\u201313 Scottish Second Division|2012\u201313]]\n\n;Raith Rovers\n*[[Scottish Challenge Cup]] (1): [[2014 Scottish Challenge Cup Final|2013\u201314]]\n\n===Individual===\n*SFL Goalkeeper of the Season Award (1): 2012\u201313\n*[[PFA Scotland Team of the Year]] (1): 2012\u201313\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{2012\u201313 PFA Scotland Second Division Team of the Year}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Robinson, Lee}}\n[[Category:1986 