inda Purl\n*''[[French Silk]]'', Susan Lucci, Lee Horsley\n*''[[Mercy Mission - the Rescue of Flight 771|Mercy Mission: The Rescue of Flight 771]]'', CBS: Robert Loggia, Scott Bakula\n*''[[Geronimo (film)|Geronimo]]'', TNT: Joseph Runningfox\n*''[[Zelda (film)|Zelda]]'', TNT: Natasha Richardson, Timothy Hutton\n*''[[Murder in the Heartland]]'', Tim Roth, Fairuza Balk\n*''[[List of Hallmark Hall of Fame episodes#Season 42 (1992-1993)|Blind Spot]]'', Hallmark Hall of Fame \u2013 CBS: Joanne Woodward, Laura Linney\n*''[[Jewels (miniseries)|Jewels]]'', CBS: Annette O'Toole, Anthony Andrews\n*''[[In Broad Daylight (1991 film)|In Broad Daylight]]'', NBC: Brian Dennehy, Marcia Gay Harden\n*''[[Her Hidden Truth]]', NBC: Kellie Martin, Antonio Sabato Jr.\n\n==Television series credits==\nThis is a partial list.\n\n*''[[Monk (TV series)|Monk]]''\n*''Extreme''\n*''Black Tie Affair''\n*''Baltimore''\n*''Cutters''\n*''[[The Days and Nights of Molly Dodd]]'' (theme and episode scores)\n*''[[The Simpsons]]'': \"[[Simpson and Delilah]]\"\n*''[[The Slap Maxwell Story]]''\n*''FM''\n*''[[AfterMASH]]''\n*''[[Columbo (TV series)|Columbo]]''\n*''[[Lou Grant (TV series)|Lou Grant]]''\n*''[[The Streets of San Francisco]]'' (theme and 11 scores)\n*''[[The Bob Newhart Show]]''\n*''[[The Mary Tyler Moore Show]]''\n*''[[The Tony Randall Show]]''\n*''[[The Magician (U.S. TV series)|The Magician]]''\n*''[[Hercules (TV miniseries)|Hercules]]''\n*''[[The Music Scene (TV series)|The Music Scene]]''\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official website|http://www.patrickwilliamsmusic.com/}}\n*{{Allmusic |class=artist |id=patrick-williams-mn0000016620}}\n*{{Discogs artist|255279-Patrick-Williams|Patrick Williams}}\n* {{IMDb name|id=0002305|name=Patrick Williams}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Williams, Patrick}}\n[[Category:1939 births]]\n[[Category:2018 deaths]]\n[[Category:20th-century American composers]]\n[[Category:20th-century American conductors (music)]]\n[[Ca