fferent from country parameter. -->\n| first_aired              = {{Start date|2019|10|12|df=yes}}\n| last_aired               = {{End date|2019|12|28|df=yes}}\n| website                  = https://www.gmm25.com/shows_detail.html?id=833\n| website_title            = GMM 25 Show Details\n| production_website       = https://tv.line.me/darkbluekiss\n| production_website_title = Dark Blue Kiss \u0e08\u0e39\u0e1a\u0e2a\u0e38\u0e14\u0e17\u0e49\u0e32\u0e22\u0e40\u0e1e\u0e37\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e19\u0e32\u0e22\u0e04\u0e19\u0e40\u0e14\u0e35\u0e22\u0e27 - LINE TV\n| based_on                 = {{based on|''Dark Blue Kiss \u0e23\u0e31\u0e01\u0e44\u0e21\u0e48\u0e23\u0e30\u0e1a\u0e38\u0e2a\u0e16\u0e32\u0e19\u0e30''|Hideko Sunshine}}\n}}\n\n'''''Dark Blue Kiss''''' ({{lang-th|\u0e08\u0e39\u0e1a\u0e2a\u0e38\u0e14\u0e17\u0e49\u0e32\u0e22\u0e40\u0e1e\u0e37\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e19\u0e32\u0e22\u0e04\u0e19\u0e40\u0e14\u0e35\u0e22\u0e27}}; {{RTGS|''Chup Sut Thai Phuea Nai Khon Diao''}}), is a 2019 [[Thailand|Thai]] [[Romance film|romantic]] [[comedy-drama]] [[television series]] starring [[Tawan Vihokratana]] (Tay), [[Thitipoom Techaapaikhun]] (New), [[Supakorn Sriphotong]] (Podd), [[Gawin Caskey]] (Fluke) and [[Chayapol Jutamat]] (AJ). The series, directed by Backaof Aof Noppharnach and produced by [[GMMTV]], premiered in [[Thailand]] and aired on [[GMM 25]] from October 12, 2019 to December 28, 2019 with repeats on [[Line TV|LINE TV]].<ref>{{cite web |title=\u0e08\u0e32\u0e01\u0e2b\u0e19\u0e31\u0e07\u0e2a\u0e37\u0e2d\u0e19\u0e34\u0e22\u0e32\u0e22\u0e41\u0e08\u0e48\u0e21\u0e43\u0e2a \u0e40\u0e2d\u0e40\u0e27\u0e2d\u0e23\u0e4c\u0e27\u0e32\u0e22\u0e2a\u0e39\u0e48 \u0e0b\u0e35\u0e23\u0e35\u0e2a\u0e4c\u0e43\u0e2b\u0e21\u0e48 \u0e1b\u0e35 2019 |url=https://www.naiin.com/news-activities/2266 |website=naiin.com |accessdate=13 November 2019 |language=Thai}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=\"Dark Blue Kiss \u0e08\u0e39\u0e1a\u0e2a\u0e38\u0e14\u0e17\u0e49\u0e32\u0e22\u0e40\u0e1e\u0e37\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e19\u0e32\u0e22\u0e04\u0e19\u0e40\u0e14\u0e35\u0e22\u0e27\" \u0e40\u0e15\u0e23\u0e35\u0e22\u0e21\u0e1f\u0e34\u0e19\u0e40\u0e15\u0e47\u0e21\u0e2a\u0e39\u0e1a! |url=https://www.sanook.com/movie/91229/ |website=sanook.com |accessdate=13 November 2019 |language=Thai}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=\"\u0e40\u0e15\" \u0e2d\u0e2d\u0e01\u0e42\u0e23\u0e07\u0e0a\u0e48\u0e27\u0e22 \"\u0e19\u0e34\u0e27\" \u0e07\u0e31\u0e14\u0e2b\u0e25\u0e31\u0e01\u0e10\u0e32\u0e19\u0e44\u0e25\u0e1f\u0e4c\u0e2a\u0e14!!! |url=https://www.newsplus.co.th/181662 |website=newsplus.co.th |publisher=News Plus |accessdate=7 April 2020 |language=Thai |date=28 December 2019}}</ref>\n\nIt was one of the 13 television series for 2019 launched by GMMTV in their \"Wonder Th13teen\" event last November 5, 2018.<ref>{{cite web |title=\u0e40\u0e1b\u0e34\u0e14\u0e15\u0e31\u0e27 13 \u0e0b\u0e35\u0e23\u0e35\u0e2a\u0e4c\u0e43\u0e2b\u0e21\u0e48 2019 \u0e41\u0e1f\u0e19\u0e46 \u0e2a\u0e32\u0e22\u0e27\u0e32\u0e22\u0e40\u0e15\u0e23\u0e35\u0e22\u0e21\u0e15\u0e31\u0e27\u0e1f\u0e34\u0e19\u0e15\u0e25\u0e2d\u0e14\u0e17\u0e31\u0e49\u0e07\u0e1b\u0e35 |url=http://www.thaiticketmajor.com/variety/ent/10470/ |website=thaiticketmajor.com |accessdate=12 December 2019 |language=Thai}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=\u201c\u0e08\u0e35\u0e40\u0e2d\u0e47\u0e21\u0e40\u0e2d\u0e47\u0e21\u0e17\u0e35\u0e27\u0e35\u201d \u0e08\u0e31\u0e14\u0e43\u0e2b\u0e0d\u0e48 \u0e40\u0e1b\u0e34\u0e14\u0e15\u0e31\u0e27 13 \u0e0b\u0e35\u0e23\u0e35\u0e2a\u0e4c\u0e43\u0e2b\u0e21\u0e48 \u0e1b\u0e35 2019 |url=https://www.springnews.co.th/entertain/fiction/378681 |website=springnews.co.th |publisher=[[Spring News]] |accessdate=12 December 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Synopsis ==\nTaking off from the [[Kiss Me Again (Thai TV series)|Kiss Me Again]] series, Pete ([[Tawan Vihokratana]]) and Kao ([[Thitipoom Techaapaikhun]]), who is still closeted from his mother, have grown closer to each other in their relationship. As Kao's sister goes to college, he supports his mom financially by doing part-time tutoring to high school students. The director of the school where his mom works asks Kao to tutor his son, Non ([[Chayapol Jutamat]]), after hearing that he is a good tutor. Pete crosses paths with Non in a competition and pisses him off after learning that Kao is tutoring him. With Non fueling Pete's jealousy, his relationship with Kao gets tested in several occasions.\n\nSun ([[Supakorn Sriphotong]]), who was pursuing Kao before, has been nagging Mork ([[Gawin Caskey]]) for dragging his younger brother, Rain ([[Pluem Pongpisal]]) into his troubles. To help him change his life, Sun offers Mork a job in his caf\u00e9. Along the way, the two of them start to care for each other. However, with Mork's dangerous life still troubling him, Sun makes it clear that he is there because he cares for him.\n\n== Cast and characters ==\nBelow are the cast of the series:<ref>{{cite web |title=TV Time - Dark Blue Kiss (TVShow Time) |url=https://www.tvtime.com/en/show/355366 |website=tvtime.com |accessdate=13 November 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Dark Blue Kiss EngSub (2019) |url=https://wvw.newasiantv.tv/drama/dark-blue-kiss.6602.html |website=newasiantv.tv |accessdate=13 November 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Dark Blue Kiss \u0e08\u0e39\u0e1a\u0e2a\u0e38\u0e14\u0e17\u0e49\u0e32\u0e22\u0e40\u0e1e\u0e37\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e19\u0e32\u0e22\u0e04\u0e19\u0e40\u0e14\u0e35\u0e22\u0e27 - Official Trailer [Eng Sub] |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zRr2QTHukzo |website=youtube.com |publisher=[[GMMTV]] |accessdate=7 April 2020 |date=27 September 2019}}</ref>\n=== Main ===\n* [[Tawan Vihokratana]] (Tay) as Pete \n* [[Thitipoom Techaapaikhun]] (New) as Kao\n* [[Supakorn Sriphotong]] (Podd) as Sun\n* [[Gawin Caskey]] (Fluke) as Mork\n* [[Chayapol Jutamat]] (AJ) as Non\n\n=== Supporting ===\n* [[Pluem Pongpisal]] as Rain\n* [[Lapassalan Jiravechsoontornkul]] (Mild) as Sandee\n* [[Jirakit Thawornwong]] (Mek) as Thada\n* [[Nachat Juntapun]] (Nicky) as June\n* [[Patchatorn Thanawat]] (Ploy) as Manow\n* [[Lapisara Intarasut]] (Apple) as Kitty\n* [[Krittaphat Chanthanaphot]] as Pete's father\n* [[Benja Singkharawat]] (Yangyi) as Kao's mother\n* [[Paramej Noiam]] as Non's father\n\n=== Guest role ===\n* [[Thanaboon Wanlopsirinun]] (Na) as barista\n* [[Phuwin Tangsakyuen]]\n* [[Trai Nimtawat]] (Neo)\n\n==Soundtracks==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Song Title\n!Romanized Title\n!Artist(s)\n!Ref\n|-\n| ''\u0e44\u0e21\u0e48\u0e21\u0e35\u0e19\u0e34\u0e22\u0e32\u0e21''\n| ''Mai Mi Ni-yam''\n| [[Tawan Vihokratana]] (Tay)<br>[[Thitipoom Techaapaikhun]] (New)\n| <ref>{{cite web |title=\u0e44\u0e21\u0e48\u0e21\u0e35\u0e19\u0e34\u0e22\u0e32\u0e21 Ost.Dark Blue Kiss \u0e08\u0e39\u0e1a\u0e2a\u0e38\u0e14\u0e17\u0e49\u0e32\u0e22\u0e40\u0e1e\u0e37\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e19\u0e32\u0e22\u0e04\u0e19\u0e40\u0e14\u0e35\u0e22\u0e27 |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tKagDmtq49I |website=youtube.com |publisher=[[GMMTV]] Records |accessdate=19 November 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''\u0e15\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e43\u0e2b\u0e49\u0e40\u0e1b\u0e47\u0e19\u0e08\u0e39\u0e1a\u0e2a\u0e38\u0e14\u0e17\u0e49\u0e32\u0e22''\n| ''To Hai Pen Chup Sut Thai''\n| [[Gawin Caskey]] (Fluke)\n| <ref>{{cite web |title=\u0e15\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e43\u0e2b\u0e49\u0e40\u0e1b\u0e47\u0e19\u0e08\u0e39\u0e1a\u0e2a\u0e38\u0e14\u0e17\u0e49\u0e32\u0e22 Ost.Dark Blue Kiss \u0e08\u0e39\u0e1a\u0e2a\u0e38\u0e14\u0e17\u0e49\u0e32\u0e22\u0e40\u0e1e\u0e37\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e19\u0e32\u0e22\u0e04\u0e19\u0e40\u0e14\u0e35\u0e22\u0e27 |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b9T6hF0WoAc |website=youtube.com |publisher=[[GMMTV]] Records |accessdate=19 November 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== Reception ==\nOn December 24, 2019, GMMTV announced a fan meeting event dubbed as ''\"POLCA The Journey: Tay & New 1st Fan Meeting in Thailand\"'' scheduled for March 21, 2020 at Chaengwattana Hall, [[CentralPlaza Chaengwattana]] featuring the series' main casts.<ref>{{cite web |title=\"POLCA THE JOURNEY\" TAY & NEW 1st FAN MEETING IN THAILAND |url=https://www.facebook.com/gmmtvofficial/posts/10157571108601224 |website=facebook.com |publisher=[[GMMTV]] |accessdate=7 April 2020 |date=24 December 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=\"POLCA THE JOURNEY\" TAY & NEW 1st FAN MEETING IN THAILAND |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aahwmuIGoLE |website=youtube.com |publisher=[[GMMTV]] |accessdate=7 April 2020 |language=Thai |date=24 December 2019}}</ref> However, due to [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Thailand|COVID-19 pandemic]] concerns, the said event was postponed and was rescheduled to August 1, 2020.<ref>{{cite web |title=[ \u0e40\u0e25\u0e37\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e19\u0e01\u0e32\u0e23\u0e41\u0e2a\u0e14\u0e07 ] \"POLCA THE JOURNEY\" TAY & NEW 1ST FAN MEETING IN THAILAND (\u0e02\u0e22\u0e32\u0e22\u0e27\u0e31\u0e19\u0e04\u0e37\u0e19\u0e40\u0e07\u0e34\u0e19) |url=https://www.thaiticketmajor.com/variety/announcement/12882/ |website=thaiticketmajor.com |accessdate=7 April 2020 |language=Thai |date=19 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n== Awards and nominations ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+\n!Year\n!Award Ceremony\n!Category\n!Recipient(s)\n!Result\n!Ref\n|-\n| rowspan=\"10\" |2020\n| LINE TV Awards 2020\n| Best Couple\n| [[Tawan Vihokratana]] (Tay)<br>[[Thitipoom Techaapaikhun]] (New)\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref>{{cite web |title=LINE TV AWARDS 2020 \u0e23\u0e32\u0e07\u0e27\u0e31\u0e25\u0e43\u0e19\u0e1b\u0e35\u0e19\u0e35\u0e49\u0e08\u0e30\u0e40\u0e1b\u0e47\u0e19\u0e02\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e43\u0e04\u0e23 |url=https://www.beartai.com/lifestyle/404837 |website=beartai.com |publisher=Beartai |accessdate=7 April 2020 |language=Thai |date=15 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=\u0e2a\u0e23\u0e38\u0e1b\u0e1c\u0e25\u0e23\u0e32\u0e07\u0e27\u0e31\u0e25 LINE TV AWARDS 2020 \u0e01\u0e25\u0e31\u0e1f-\u0e21\u0e34\u0e27, \u0e42\u0e2d\u0e21-\u0e2a\u0e34\u0e07\u0e42\u0e15, \u0e2d\u0e2d\u0e1f-\u0e01\u0e31\u0e19 \u0e41\u0e25\u0e30\u0e1a\u0e49\u0e32\u0e19\u0e19\u0e32\u0e14\u0e32\u0e27 \u0e04\u0e27\u0e49\u0e32\u0e23\u0e32\u0e07\u0e27\u0e31\u0e25\u0e40\u0e23\u0e35\u0e22\u0e01\u0e40\u0e2a\u0e35\u